SYNOPSIS
    int P_PAGESIZE  "PageSize"

    int Set(P_PAGESIZE, int value)
    int Query(P_PAGESIZE)
      or
    int SetPageSize(int value)
    int QueryPageSize()

DESCRIPTION
    The pagesize for the interactive user.

EXAMPLE
    Query(P_PAGESIZE);

AVAILABILITY
    Include: <properties.h>

    Availability: /std/player(/filesys)

SEE ALSO
    player(S)
